  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--1938-- that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that the looting and everything started, and that we went-- my mother, my sister, and I went to the house of friends of ours, not far from our house that we were living in then, in Berlin, and hid out there.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were shown-- this was located in a sort of private park, or a large garden, if you will.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the gates had to be opened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anybody that wanted to come in had the-- had to have the, the garden gates to open, so the drive-- so then they could drive to the house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it wasn't easy to, to get there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still, to this day, don't-- I have a false memory of this because the memory I have is of some friends of ours who were Jewish, who were called Simon and who had a house, something like that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My memory is that we were in that house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it can't be because they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, that-- that's really beside the point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The point is that we were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father was-- we had no idea where he was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was with friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He didn't want us to know, in case we were asked and questioned in, in forceful ways.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so we didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we saw each other again at our house, about four days later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that is also when the regulations came into force about the professions that I mentioned before, about Jewish doctors and Jewish lawyers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I should also add that-- you were asking what other measures there had been, prior to that, that made life difficult.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
